## Ifya kucita no bubifi mu cilonganino
## Ubupyungishi bwa Bamalaika
## “Natuleya!” ya kuntanshi
## Muli uno mwaka tulinokumona ukuya kwa ba Editor balipo.
## Lesa alebatungulula pamo nolupwa lwabo ukubwelelamo ku Germany uko bali nokuibimba muku kansha kwa ntungulushi sha munkuta nefya buminshoni.
## Ici tacishile mukupumikisha, lelo kukwambafye bamunyinefwe abaibimbamo balyesha ukushimpa uyu mulimo munshila iwingakonkanyapo nokubomba pa myaka iingi ukwabula ukushintilila pa muntu uuli
onse uleutungilila. 
## Lelo fyonse fibili, ukulolesha kunuma elyo nakuntanshi, 
## nacilenga intungulushi sha uyu mulimo ukutontonkanyapo bwino bwino nokutantika ifintu fimo ifilingile ukucinjishiwa pakuti magazine ingatwalilila kuntanshi.
## Nanomba tatulakumanisha bamunyinefwe nenkashi isha uyu mulimo.
## Pamulandu waici, casuminishiwe ukusankanya amabumba yabili, ilya lelolekesha pali “Natuleya!” elyo nelya “Inkosho”.
## Ibumba lipya ilya bampandamano nomba lipangilwe na bamunyinefwe 6, nabambi 4 abalebomba ngaba Coordinator mufitungu babelele (moneni pebula 30). 
## Tulelolekesha pakulundapo nabambi, maka maka inkashi shili ishapokelelwa ukuilunda kuli ifwe. 
## Elyo napa provincial Level, ba coordinator kuti bakabila incenshi intungulushi ishakubatungilila.
## Nangula cili icakutila ba Editor balipo bali abaiteyanya ukukonkanyapo ukuibimba mukupanga kwa iyi magazine ilyo bakaba ku Germany ukupitila mukubomfya email
## elyo nokulaisa libili libili ku Zambia, 
## twasalile ukufwaya bamunyinefwe abo bengakwanisha ukubuula imilimo imo iyo babomba.
## Ibumba lilolekesha pa fitabo mu Kasama nalisumina ukukonkanyapo umulimo wakuprinta no kupwishisha magazine kuntanshi.
## Lelo mufifulo tulefwaya ukubika bambi, mukwai moneni ilyashi pebula 30.
## Tulekabila ukusha ubusuma bwa magazine kuli bakabelenga.
## Kukusenamina kwakwa Lesa, bamunyinefwe aba mu Germany balilenga twakwanisha ukushita mashini iikalamba kabili iyangufyanya ukuprinta amapepala. 
## Ngefyo mumwene magazine ili muminwe yenu, ilekwanisha ukuprinta pepepala ilikulu (A3), kabili nefikope filemonekako bwino nomba.
## Pakuti twingabikamo amalyashi yalekana lekana, twakulapanga amagazine aya mundimi shibili, imo mu Cibemba imbi nayo mu Cingeleshi. 
## Icikasha incende yakubikapo amalyashi nayambi muli cila lulimi. 
## Elyo twalikonka nefyo bakabelenga bamo bamo batwebele ukutila twingasansha “Natuleya!” ne “Ikosho” nokukwatafye magazine imo kuntanshi lelo isuma. 
## Kuli abo baleumfwa bwino sana ukubelenga magazine iikwete indimi shibili bakakonkanyapo ukuilako pantanshi mukusambilila ukupitila mukushita yonse yabili – amalyashi ayengi yakatwalilila ukuba cimo cine.
## Tulekabila ukubweshako umutengo wakupangila.
## Umutengo wamapepala, inki nemweseshe ilenina inshita yonse. 
## Pantu tulefwaya kutuula imilimo mu lubali lwa milembele, ukutwala mululimi lumbi, nemipangile ya magazine pamabeya ya bantu abengi, tulekabila ukufushishako indalama ishakubomfya.
## Ilangi lya nkupo nga iyi ili mumwinwe yenu isenda indalama ukufika kucipendo 45% ishacipendo tupangila. 
## Twasalile ku nshita ileisa ukulaipanga pamutengo uwapanshi kabili munshila iya yanguka pakutila tatwishile ninika umutengo wakulaishitishapo. 
## Indume shamu Kasama shili nokukonkanyapo ukufwaya ama volunteers (bakubomba lutu) mukubika amapepala ya magazine capamo mukutwalilila ukulenga umutengo wakushitishishapo panshi kuli bakabelenga.
## Tulekabila ukufuntulako ukusalanganya
## Ukushitisha magazine ukupitila mu filonganino cikankala, kabili tulinokukonkanyapo ukucita ici. 
## Lelo twasangile ukutila ninshila imo ibombeka panono panono, kabili cipendo ca bantu fye abanono abashita.
## Pakuti twingacefyanyako imibomfeshe yandalama, tulingile ukumona ukuti amagazine ayengi yaleshitishiwa. 
## Pamulandu wa ici, natukushako indalama yakupeelamo abo bakalashitisha magazine. 
## Tukalabombela pamo nama Coordinators elyo nama Distributors ukumona ifyo twingafuntula imisabankanishe ya magazine mu ncende shabo. 
## Nga cakutila muli cila District twakwete umuntu umo “Kashitisha uwamaka” uuleshitisha ayali 100 pali cila magazine, 
## kuti indalama shailako imiku itatu pamulu nokulenga magazine yesu ukwishibikwa sana ukucila ifyo yaishibikwa pali nomba. 
## Mulandu nshi ba “The Post” beka nangula bakashitisha wamapepala bambi ebofye balesanga abantu abaipeelesha ukushitisha? 
## Ulukuta mu Zambia icinefye lwalikwata abantu abo lwingapeela abengabomba bwino amakwebo, teifyo fine? 
## Tulekabila abantu abashilesakama pakulamfya insapato shabo. 
## Natubombele pamo! Kuti mwaisawamya insapato shenu limbi. 
## Cikulufye kuti mwakwanisha ukwendauka, ukutwafwa ukusabankanya ukwishibikwa kwacine cakwa Lesa mu ncende tubelele!
## Kuli abo abakotele sana or abashingakwanisha mukushitisha, twabikamo ipepala lya musangulo (Donation Slip) muli iyi magazine. 
## Ikumikeniko kumapaalo yakwa Lesa mwitumba lyenu nabo bakalabomba ngaba Editor, Translator nangu abakwanshika ifyo magazine ikalamoneka kuntanshi.
## Nangu afweni ukulipila indalama shapa ofeshi nefikumine fya milanshanishishe.
